data.description: This wonderful spacious pool home in the foothill area enjoys mature landscaping & gorgeous mountain views. There are many important factors to know about this wonderful property. The most relevant being that it is on a third of an acre with opportunity to add a casita or additional garage in the currently unused 50' x 75' portion of level land behind the pool.  The primary suite is large, open & offers a jacuzzi for you to relax & unwind. The air conditioned garage has an additional room in the back perfect for an office. The wall could easily be removed for a 30' deep garage. Numerous upgrades have been completed recently, too many to mention here. A handful of these include: Gunite pool has been replastered, new pool plumbing and cool decking. Swamp coolers have been removed & roof was replaced in 2022. New mini-split in garage. All windows have been re-screened & re-tinted. Exterior of home & block walls have new paint.  This home offers the perfect blend of comfort & functionality, located in a quiet, sought-after area of Lake Havasu City.
